            "heading_tag": "h4",
            "icon": "plant",
            "no_padding": true,
            "content": "<p>Our Refuel Protein-Rich, Plant-Based Food offers a variety of benefits. It's packed with high-quality plant-based protein to support muscle growth and recovery, and it's enriched with essential vitamins and minerals to boost your overall health. Plus, it's made from all-natural ingredients, free from artificial additives, and is easy to digest, making it a perfect addition to any balanced diet.</p>",
