            "heading": "Shipping & Returns",
            "tab_image_width": 1000,
            "hide_image": false,
            "row_content": "<h2>Returns policy</h2><ul><li>Dispatch: Within 24 Hours</li><li>Free shipping across all products on a minimum purchase of $50.</li><li>International delivery time - 7-10 business days</li><li>Cash on delivery might be available</li><li>Easy 30 days returns and exchanges</li></ul><h2>Shipping policy</h2><p>We offer standard and expedited shipping options at checkout. Standard shipping typically takes 3-7 business days, while expedited shipping arrives in 2-3 business days. Shipping costs are calculated based on the weight of the order and the selected shipping method. Free standard shipping is available on orders over $50.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
